COVID GLUE snp to lineage and taxon map

Source: R/cov_glue_lineage_data.R
cov_glue_snp_lineage.Rd

This function maps lineage name to snps and to taxon names. Everything is GISAID-specific.

cov_glue_snp_lineage()

Value

a data.frame

References

  • https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.04.17.046086v1
